To use tools such as virt-manager or virsh in a standard user mode, your
user must be in the group libvirtd.

    sudo gpasswd -a myuser libvirtd 
    su myuser
    newgrp libvirtd

Edit your /etc/nixos/configuration.nix and addÂ :

